name: Nguyen Quang Hai
description: Nguyễn Quang Hải (born 12 April 1997) is a Vietnamese professional footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder for Hà Nội and Vietnam national football team. In 2018, he was voted by a panel of sports journalists and football experts as among the top 15 of Best Footballer in Asia. In 2019, he was voted as among the top 17 best footballers in Asia. He is considered one of the best Vietnamese footballers of his generation.
